{"tid":2363938,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯儲2020年向財政部上繳利潤885億美元 驟增近三分之二！","createTime":"2021-01-12T14:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T15:43:30.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"acb691828d9c4098f21534ccd1c747c07afa08d7","tid":2363938,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"2020年美聯儲給美國財政部帶來了885億美元的利潤，較上年增加了近三分之二，原因是低利率減少了美聯儲的利息支出。<br />\n<br />\n  美聯儲（FED）週一發布的報告顯示，2020年其向美國財政部上繳的利潤較上年驟增333億美元，增幅近三分之二，至885億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/finance/crawl/120/w550h370/20210112/1403-khmynua7120659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ffinance%2Fcrawl%2F120%2Fw550h370%2F20210112%2F1403-khmynua7120659.jpg&h=d0be0106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">這主要得益於較低利率減少了美聯儲的利息支出，而淨收入主要來自通過公開市場操作獲得的證券利息收入1000億美元。</span><br />\n<br />\n  此外，在運營費用方面，扣除美國財政部和其他實體因儲備銀行作為財政代理提供的服務而償還的費用，總計為45億美元。 2020年，為應對新冠肺炎大流行造成的經濟低迷，美聯儲將利率降至接近零的水平，大幅降低了銀行超額準備金的利息支付。<br />\n<br />\n  關於收入的使用方面，美聯儲被要求用其收入來支付運營費用，並將大部分剩餘收入存入財政部的普通基金（general fund），用於幫助支付政府的賬單。<br />\n<br />\n  週一的數據為初步數據，美聯儲可能在3月公佈經審計的財務報表時進行修正。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B22020%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%91%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%B9%B3885%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%88%A9%E6%BD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%AF%94%E5%A2%9E%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C-11610409611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2584%25B22020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B9%25B3885%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%25BD%25A4%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25BA%258C-11610409611&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJufroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=2075e9ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B22020%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%91%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%B9%B3885%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%88%A9%E6%BD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%AF%94%E5%A2%9E%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C-11610409611</a>"},{"pid":"26e5635e43b5351bb46e6e22185716ee4736a65f","tid":2363938,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"美國回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c1c18181152421ab04b2930c45a5de0d8de39d","tid":2363938,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"咪又係自己印出黎"}]}